Benefits:

Have fun with this modeling mask that comes in a cute shake design complete with a "lid" and "straw" that serves as the spatula. Available in four different types enriched with power ingredients such as hyaluronic acid for hydration, glutathione for brightening, alpinia leaf to calm sensitive skin, and alpha-lipoic acid to restore firmness and elasticity. The modeling pack helps in optimal absorption of essence to nourish, hydrate, and restore firmness and radiance to skin. Mix the booster and ampoule in the cup. Close the lid and shake well until fully mixed. Use the spatula to apply on cleansed and toned skin. Peel off mask after 20 minutes. Remove any excess with a damp cotton pad.
Hydro shot - contains hyaluronic acid to give skin a moisturizing glow. 
Soothing shot - contains alpinia to calm sensitive skin.
Luminous shot - contains glutathione to brighten dull skin. 
Elastic Shot - contains alpha-lipoic acid that restores firmness to loose skin.

How to Use:

Remove the lid and spatula from the shaking cup.
Pour the Double Trans Booster (1) and Ampoule (2) into the shaking the cup and cover with the lid. Block the hole on the lid with your finger and shake the cup until all the contents are mixed evenly. 
As soon as the mixture turns into cream, use the provided spatula to spread the mask evenly all over your face, avoiding the eye and lip areas. 
After 15-20 minutes or when the mask hardens, gently peel off the sheet starting from the edges.
Wipe off any residue and continue with your skin care routine. 

Colors Available:

Hydro Shot
Soothing Shot
Luminous Shot
Elastic Shot

About brand: Dr. Jart+
Dr. Jart+ is the leading Korean skin care brand known for bringing BB creams to the global market. Established in 2005 by dermatologist Jung Sung-jae and entrepreneur Lee Chin-wook, the brand is backed by a team of dermatologists affiliated with leading universities and clinics across Korea. Dr. Jart+ continues to create innovative skin care solutions including its Cicapair Tiger Grass, Ceramidin, V7, Dermask, Water Jet, Dermaclear and Every Sun Day series. Among its bestselling products are the Dermask Solution sheet masks, Ceramidin Cream, Cicapair Calming Gel Cream and Cryo Rubber masks. All Dr. Jart+ products are made in Korea.

Benefits:

Have fun with this modeling mask that comes in a cute shake design complete with a "lid" and "straw" that serves as the spatula. Available in four different types enriched with power ingredients such as hyaluronic acid for hydration, glutathione for brightening, alpinia leaf to calm sensitive skin, and alpha-lipoic acid to restore firmness and elasticity. The modeling pack helps in optimal absorption of essence to nourish, hydrate, and restore firmness and radiance to skin. Mix the booster and ampoule in the cup. Close the lid and shake well until fully mixed. Use the spatula to apply on cleansed and toned skin. Peel off mask after 20 minutes. Remove any excess with a damp cotton pad.
Hydro shot - contains hyaluronic acid to give skin a moisturizing glow. 
Soothing shot - contains alpinia to calm sensitive skin.
Luminous shot - contains glutathione to brighten dull skin. 
Elastic Shot - contains alpha-lipoic acid that restores firmness to loose skin.

How to Use:

Remove the lid and spatula from the shaking cup.
Pour the Double Trans Booster (1) and Ampoule (2) into the shaking the cup and cover with the lid. Block the hole on the lid with your finger and shake the cup until all the contents are mixed evenly. 
As soon as the mixture turns into cream, use the provided spatula to spread the mask evenly all over your face, avoiding the eye and lip areas. 
After 15-20 minutes or when the mask hardens, gently peel off the sheet starting from the edges.
Wipe off any residue and continue with your skin care routine.

About brand: Dr. Jart+
Dr. Jart+ is the leading Korean skin care brand known for bringing BB creams to the global market. Established in 2005 by dermatologist Jung Sung-jae and entrepreneur Lee Chin-wook, the brand is backed by a team of dermatologists affiliated with leading universities and clinics across Korea. Dr. Jart+ continues to create innovative skin care solutions including its Cicapair Tiger Grass, Ceramidin, V7, Dermask, Water Jet, Dermaclear and Every Sun Day series. Among its bestselling products are the Dermask Solution sheet masks, Ceramidin Cream, Cicapair Calming Gel Cream and Cryo Rubber masks. All Dr. Jart+ products are made in Korea.

About brand: make p:rem
Adopting the Nordic lagom concept meaning “just the right amount”, Korean brand make p:rem simplifies skin care routines with its multifunctional products. The brand’s collection uses highly pure natural ingredients like Arctic raspberry extract, Finnish birch sap and peat water from Denmark, and counts on the brand’s patented Micro Trans Moisture Technology to effectively deliver them into skin. Packaging and ingredient quantity are kept minimal, reflecting the "just right" philosophy. All products are made in Korea. YesStyle is an authorized retailer of make p:rem.

About brand: innisfree
innisfree offers Korean skin care that harmoniously combines pure and natural ingredients with an eco-friendly philosophy. From pore-clearing clay masks with super volcanic clusters to intensive hydrating eye creams, the Korean beauty brand's vast array of skin care and makeup products make use of vegetable, fruit and mineral ingredients, such as green tea, marine seaweed, black tea, cherry blossom and volcanic clay from South Korea's mineral-rich Jeju Island. innisfree engages in fair trade practices to promote higher environmental standards and sustainability. Some of the brand's bestsellers include the Super Volcanic Pore Clay Mask 2X, Green Tea Seed Serum, Canola Honey Lip Balm and No Sebum Mineral Powder. The innisfree Jeju Orchid, Blueberry Rebalancing and My Real Squeeze Mask lines are also very popular with customers.

About brand: Manyo
Skin care brand Manyo (an abbreviation of Manyo Factory) creates all its products in Korea based on a unique “10-Ups” philosophy, which promotes benefits such as “Tone Up,” “Softening Up” and “Condition Up.” To ensure products are suitable for various skin types, the brand incorporates only essential ingredients that are beneficial to skin. Bestsellers include the nourishing and refreshing Pure Cleansing Oil and the Galactomy Niacin Essence, which contains 97% galactomyces ferment filtrate. YesStyle is an authorized retailer of Manyo.
